165.3532, 165.0277, 165.1628, 165.0424, 164.6215, 165.4895, 164.7067, 164.7997, 165.8066, 166.0475, 167.1314, 167.8707, 167.8683, 167.2996, 167.8282, 167.7574, 167.9075, 168.5004, 169.1446, 168.9572, 168.7709, 168.0634, 165.8835, 167.0115, 167.3991, 166.8631, 166.9008, 166.5562, 164.8502, 165.3563, 165.5671, 166.499, 165.9298, 165.6174, 165.7802, 165.4062, 166.1249, 167.3409, 167.8484, 167.9891, 167.9444, 167.5261, 166.3743, 165.9501, 166.0525, 164.9953, 164.7487, 165.3671, 165.7007, 166.4571, 166.8493, 167.0204, 167.0076, 168.087, 166.6231, 167.1766, 167.111, 167.9175, 167.8078, 167.3876, 167.043, 166.5934, 166.7082, 168.018, 168.2707, 167.5665, 168.4133, 169.0736, 169.8212, 169.4826, 169.8917, 169.557, 169.3575, 169.1958, 169.0043, 169.056, 168.8936, 168.5649, 168.2049, 168.7226, 168.5322, 169.1179, 169.1178, 168.5114, 169.4923, 170.1282, 170.2758, 169.8813, 169.0349, 169.1516, 168.106, 168.5799, 170.4432, 169.9103, 169.1983, 170.1915, 170.5987, 170.9024, 170.1755, 170.1288, 171.2554, 169.9894, 168.6392, 168.8819, 168.8018, 168.9326, 170.8887, 170.1572, 170.3907, 170.6887, 171.0237, 173.5733, 174.0737, 173.6986, 172.1511, 174.3914, 175.3474, 175.455, 176.4765, 176.5907, 174.1692, 174.1199, 173.1819, 174.9744, 175.4269, 174.7634, 175.3057, 176.5011, 176.4534, 176.4501, 176.7898, 177.3928, 178.3627, 179.6668, 181.6698, 182.2177, 183.4404, 181.9144, 182.2691, 183.3825, 184.3595, 182.9161, 184.1041, 182.7691, 182.3414, 182.7935, 182.9921, 181.7842, 179.7098, 177.6, 178.7077, 177.9616, 179.5233, 179.9459, 180.5564, 181.416, 179.2656], "summary_html": "<h1>沪铜多因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 1.08)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报以沪铜为例，从宏观、库存、利润、升贴水四大类约100个指标中筛选出23个因子（Sharpe&gt;0.5且胜率&gt;45%），对每个指标分别采用动量/单均线/双均线/历史分位数策略构建交易信号。同类因子等权叠加仓位形成子策略，子策略间再等权叠加得到多因子组合。本复现将原文沪铜单品种方法推广至全品种截面，使用日频数据中的真实基本面字段（ry/basis/profit/inventory_21/receipt）替代原文外部数据源，构建四类截面因子（carry/库存/基差/利润），截面排名后等权组合形成多因子仓位。</p>\n<p>核心逻辑：基本面因子在品种截面上具有预测力（CS IC = 0.019），多因子组合通过分散化降低回撤并提升风险调整收益。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.03</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.6%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>5.4%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-12.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.04</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.13</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.17</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.4 / 0.94</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.23</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.18</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.14</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.66</span></td><td>0.62</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.53</span></td><td>0.9</td><td>1.05</td><td>1.71</td><td>1.26</td><td>1.65</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.34</span></td><td>0.43</td><td>0.44</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.41</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>profit</code></td><td>利润</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>Carry因子</strong>（使用展期收益ry）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{carry}_N^{(i,t)} = \\frac{1}{N} \\sum_{k=0}^{N-1} \\text{ry}^{(i, t-k)}, \\quad N \\in \\{20, 40, 60, 80, 120\\}</div>\n<p><strong>库存因子</strong>（inventory_21 + receipt动量，方向反转）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{inv}_N^{(i,t)} = -\\left(\\frac{\\text{inventory\\_21}^{(i,t)}}{\\text{inventory\\_21}^{(i,t-N)}} - 1\\right), \\quad N \\in \\{20, 40, 60\\}</div>\n<p><strong>基差因子</strong>（basis水平 + 双均线差值）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{basis\\_lvl}_N^{(i,t)} = \\text{MA}_N(\\text{basis}^{(i)}), \\quad \\text{basis\\_dma}_{s,l}^{(i,t)} = \\text{MA}_s(\\text{basis}^{(i)}) - \\text{MA}_l(\\text{basis}^{(i)})</div>\n<p><strong>利润因子</strong>（动量，方向反转）:</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{profit}_N^{(i,t)} = -\\left(\\frac{\\text{profit}^{(i,t)}}{\\text{profit}^{(i,t-N)}} - 1\\right), \\quad N \\in \\{20, 40, 60\\}</div>\n<p><strong>组合</strong>：各因子截面排名 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> 同类因子等权平均 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> 子策略等权叠加 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> <code>rank_to_continuous(scale=2.0)</code> 映射到 <span class=\"math-tex\">[-1, 1]</span> <span class=\"math-tex\">\\to</span> <code>rebalance_hold</code> 每H天换仓。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.991, 换手 0.536, 12变体</td><td>基线: carry(5窗口)+inv(3窗口)+basis(4窗口)+profit(2窗口), 截面排名等权组合, hold grid 5-20天</td><td>f4_h10=0.991 通过阈值</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>换手偏高, f4_h15接近f4_h10, 2016/2023年Sharpe弱</td><td>加长basis/profit窗口(+60), 扩展hold grid(h10/15/20), 加vol_target变体</td><td>Sharpe 0.991-&gt;1.077, 换手从0.536降至0.464</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>R2最优稳定, IC gate对截面因子无效</td><td>精简变体, 加f4_h12, 加IC-gate和vt多组合</td><td>Sharpe稳定1.077, IC gate反降至0.59(截面非时序), skip</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2 增加 profit_60 和 basis_lvl_60/basis_dma_20_60 更长窗口使 4-factor 组合 Sharpe 从 0.99 提升至 1.08。IC gate 在 R3 反而降低了 Sharpe（从 1.08 降至 0.59），因为该因子的 alpha 来源是截面排名而非品种内时序预测（TS IC = 0.003 接近零）。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（58个），盈利集中在 J, V, JM, P, I（黑色+化工）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10-15 天</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 时序 IC 接近 0（0.003），信号完全依赖截面排名，品种内无预测力\n<p>- 2016 年和 2023 年 Sharpe 接近 0，策略在某些宏观环境下失效 - 与因子库中 <code>gtja_bi_basis_ma20_60_H15_cs</code> 相关性 0.67（likely_redundant），但 Sharpe 低于该因子（1.08 vs 1.41） - 基本面字段非空率 20-45%，部分品种/日期缺失导致因子覆盖度有限 - 原文Sharpe 2.05针对沪铜单品种，全品种截面化后因非目标品种稀释而下降</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.995</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.85s</li>\n</ul>"}